***** How to use this? *****

Place your whole content in this folder and use the function...

$args = [
    'key1' => 'val1'
];
view( '[name-of-the-file]', $args )
view( '[name-of-the-file]', $args )

Inside of [name-of-the-file].php you can use the key of an 
array as a varibale.

echo $key1; // output val1